Subject: Path Traversal and O.S. Command Injection
 vulnerabilities in Polycom products

We have found two vulnerabilities in the following Polycom product:

 * System affected  : Polycom Web Management Interface
 * Model            : G3/HDX 8000 HD
                      
 * Software Version : Durango 2.6.0 Release - build #4740
 * Embedded Linux   : Polycom Linux Development Platform v2.14.g3

                      Other versions or models may also be affected.

Full details are described in the links provided below:

 + 01. Path Traversal on Polycom Web Management Interface:
    - http://www.tempest.com.br/advisories/tsi-adv-1201/ 

 + 02. Polycom Web Management Interface O.S. Command Injection:
    - http://www.tempest.com.br/advisories/tsi-adv-1202/

